node.text: these videos really made the dancer in me smile so hardddddddd. I am obviously heavily inspired and always create music with the dance community in mind. ANY CREATIVE KNOWS THIS. I understand that this wasn’t simple choreography all thanks to @itsbankhead but thank you guys for being up for the challenge. y’all inspire me in more ways than you know. i value you all so much and see you. 😌🤍✨🥺 @samuelmenagarcia @samit5678 @sienna.lalau @kerriemilne @zyasiaspage @zachmolton @antifischer @brookecolletti @lilkerriceb @amandalacount #WildSideDanceChallenge
